props.value: jtalk|1|jtalk|2|Oh! My bad, thought you were someone else. Whoops~
jtalk|2|jtalk|3|I'm Jeremy, and these lovely checkerboard tiles are mine~
jtalk|3|jtalk|4|I call this my home, so mind your filth, would ya?
jtalk|4|jtalk|5|You seem confused. Don't you have tiles too?
jtalk|5|jtalk|6|Look, it's alright if you only have one or two...
jtalk|8|jtalk|9|I got an extra tile lying around. I think it uh... fits your style~
jtalk|9|jtalk|10|You'll find it a bit up north. It's a little worn down but uh...
jtalk|10|jtalk|11|Try patching its holes with something and it'll be good as new~
jtalk|12|Maybe one day you'll have as many tiles as me. *wink*
jtalk|13|jtalk|14|Hey hey! So you claimed a tile. How's it feel?
jtalk|14|jtalk|15|Ya gotta start small kid, but you'll be like me in no time *wink*
jtalk|15|jtalk|16|Now let's try this for real...
